1771:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****     This section provides functions allowing to:
1772:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****       (+) Configure the commutation event in case of use of the Hall sensor interface.
1773:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****       (+) Configure Output channels for OC and PWM mode.
