1785:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim_ex.c **** /**
1786:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   * @brief  Configure the TIM commutation event sequence.
1787:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   * @note  This function is mandatory to use the commutation event in order to
1788:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *        update the configuration at each commutation detection on the TRGI input of the Timer,
1789:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *        the typical use of this feature is with the use of another Timer(interface Timer)
1790:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *        configured in Hall sensor interface, this interface Timer will generate the
